The N3 Toll Concession says trucks are blocking the route between Warden and Villiers in the Free State. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The N3 Toll Concession says trucks are blocking the route between Warden and Villiers in the Free State. The reason for the blockade is unclear. Both sides of the highway are affected. 08h05 14/06 #TrafficAlert: N3-9 Km 20.4 #Obstruction near Roadside/Reitz IC between #Warden and #Villiers in the #FreeState due to trucks blocking the road in both directions. Please approach the area with caution